         Well Magister is on crack as usual.  Of course roots don't always last for full duration with EA III.  They do however have the potential to last 20% longer than they do without.  Now what I have noticed is that I get far less early breaks on fear root.  It seems the 20% is tacked on to a minimum time or something.  Fears are lasting far longer, and the 20% longer dooming is awesome.  I don't know what you are killing for xp Smlogg, but the Katta guard never live longer than a Splurt, far less than 2.5 minutes.</P><P><b><font color=blue>Retrievil Hesevil</font id=blue></b><BR><font color=red><b>58 DE Necromancer - Tallon Zek</font id=red></b><BR><font color=blue><b>55 Iksar Necromancer - Rodcet Nife</b></font id=blue><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=333155" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=333155</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
